hadiths[30]{hadithnumber,text}:
6772,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab bhi zina karne wala zina karta hai to wo momin nahi rehta, jab bhi koi sharab peeney wala sharab peetaa hai to wo momin nahi rehta, jab bhi koi chori karne wala chori karta hai to wo momin nahi rehta, jab bhi koi lotney wala laut'taa hai ke log nazrein utha utha kar usey dekhney lagtey hain to wo momin nahi rahtaa. ''aur ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, unse Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma ne bayan kya unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah siwa lafz (نهبة‏) ke."
6773,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sharab peeney par chhadi aur jootey se maara tha aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chalis (40) kode maarey.
6774,"Nuaimaan ya ibne-Nuaimaan ko sharab ke nashe mein laya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghar mein maujood logon ko hukm diya ke unhein maarein, unhon-ne maaraa, Aqba kehtey hain main bhi un logon mein tha jinhoney usko jooton se maaraa."
6775,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Nuaimaan ya ibne- Nuaimaan ko laya gaya, wo nashe mein tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par ye na-gawar guzra aur aap ne ghar mein maujood logon ko hukm diya ke unhein maarein. chunanche logon ne unhein lakdi aur jooton se maara aur main bhi un logon mein tha jinhoney usey maara tha."
6776,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sharab peeney par chhadi aur jooton se maara tha aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chalis (40) (40 ( kode lagwaaey they.
6777,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs ko laya gaya jo sharab piye huey tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usey maaro, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ham mein kuchh wo they jinhoney usey hath se maaraa, kuchh ne jootey se maara aur kuchh ne apne kapdey se maaraa. jab mar chukey to kisi ne kaha ke Allah tujhey ruswa kare. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah ke jumley na kaho, iske maamle mein shaitan ki madad na kar."
6778,"main nahi pasand karunga ke had mein kisi ko aisi saza dun ke wo mar jaey aur phir mujhey iska ranj ho, siwa shraabii ke ke agar wo mar jaey to main uski diyat ada kar doonga kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski koi had muqarrar nahi ki thi."
6779,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke shuruati daure-khilaafat mein sharab peeney wala hamarey paas laya jata to ham apne haath, jootey aur chaadrein lekar khadey ho jatey (aur usey maartey) aakhir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne aakhiri daure-khilaafat mein sharab peeney walon ko chalis (40) kode maarey aur jab un logon ne mazeed sarkashi ki aur fisq w fujoor kya to 80 kode maarey ."
6780,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein aik shakhs, jiska naam Abdullah tha aur) himaar (ke laqab se pukaarey jatey they, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hansaatey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein sharab peeney par maara tha to unhein aik din laya gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye hukm diya aur unhein maara gaya. haaziriin mein aik sahib ne kaha : Allah is par laanat karey ! kitni martaba kaha ja chuka hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par laanat na karo Allah ki qism maine iske mutaalliq yahi jana hai ke ye Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat karta hai."
6781,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs nashe mein laya gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein maarney ka hukm diya. ham mein se kuchh ne unhein hath se maaraa, kuchh ne jootey se maara aur kuchh ne kapdey se maaraa. jab mar chukey to aik shakhs ne kaha, kya ho gaya usey ? Allah usey ruswa kare. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne bhai ke khilaf shaitan ki madad na karo."
6782,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab zina karne wala zina karta hai to wo momin nahi rehta aur isi tarah jab chor chori karta hai to wo momin nahi rahtaa.''
6783,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ne chor par laanat bheji ke aik andaa churaataa hai aur uska hath kaat liya jata hai, aik rassii churaataa hai uska hath kaat liya jata hai. Aamash ne kaha ke log khayal kartey they ke andey se murad lohey ka andaa hai aur rassii se murad aisi rassii samajhtey they jo kai dirham ki ho."
6784,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan aik majlis mein baithey they, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujh se ahad karo Allah ke sath koi Sharik nahi thahraaogey, chori nahi karogey aur zina nahi karogey aur aap ne ye aayat poori padhi '' to tum mein se jo shakhs is ahad ko pura karega uska sawab Allah ke yahan hai aur jo shakhs unmein se ghalati kar guzra aur is par usey saza hui to wo uska kaffara hai aur jo shakhs unmein se koi ghalati kar guzra aur Allah Taala ne uski parda poshii kar di to agar Allah chaahega to usey maaf kar dega aur agar chaahega to is par azab dega.''"
6785,"Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par farmaya ''haan tum log kis cheez ko sabse zyada hurmat wali samajhtey ho? '' logon ne kaha ke apne isi maheene ko. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''haan, kis Shahar ko tum sabse zyada hurmat wala samajhtey ho?'' logon ne jawab diya ke apne isi Shahar ko . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ''haan, kis din ko tum sabse zyada hurmat wala khayal kartey ho? '' logon ne kaha ke apne isi din ko . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ab farmaya '' phir bila shubah Allah ne tumharey khoon , tumharey maal aur tumhari izzaton ko hurmat wala qarar diya hai, siwa iske haq ke, jaisa ke is din ki hurmat is Shahar aur is maheene mein hai. haan ! kya maine tumhen pahuncha diyaa.'' teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur har martaba sahaba ne jawab diya ke ji haan , pahuncha diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' afsos mere baad tum kaafir na bin jana ke aik doosrey ki gardan maarney lago.''"
6786,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab bhi 2 chizon mein se aik ke ikhtiyar karne ka hukm diya gaya to aap ne unmein se aasan hi ko pasand kya, basharte ke usmein gunah ka koi pahlu na ho, agar usmein gunah ka koi pahlu hota to aap us se sabse zyada door hotey. Allah ki qism ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi apne zaatii maamle mein kisi se badla nahi liya, albatta jab Allah ki hurmaton ko todaa jata to aap Allah ke liye badla letey they."
6787,Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik aurat ki (jis par qurbani ka janwar muqaddima honey wala tha) sifarish ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum se pahley ke log isliye halaak ho gaey ke wo kamzoron par to had qaaim kartey aur buland martaba logon ko chhod detey they. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai. agar Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne bhi) chori ( ki hoti to main uska bhi hath kaat leta .
6788,"aik makhzumi aurat ka mamla jisne chori ki thi, Quraish ke logon ke liye ahmiyat ikhtiyar kar gaya aur unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se is maamle mein kon baat kar sakta hai Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwaa, jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bahut piyarey hain aur koi aap se sifarish ki himmat nahi kar sakta ? chunanche Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya tum Allah ki hadon mein sifarish karne aaey ho.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur khutba diya aur farmaya ''aey logo! tum se pahley ke log isliye gumrah ho gaey ke jab unmein koi bada aadmi chori karta to usey chhod detey lekin agar kamzor chori karta to is par had qaaim kartey they aur Allah ki qasam! agar Fatima binte-Muhammad ne bhi chori ki hoti to Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska hath zaroor kaat daaltey."
6789,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''chauthaaii Dinar ya us se zyada par hath kaat liya jaaeyga.'' is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid Zohri ke bhatijey aur Mamar ne Zohri ke waaste se ki.
6790,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' chor ka hath aik chothai Dinar par kaat liya jaaeyga.''
6791,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' chothai Dinar par hath kaataa jaaeyga.''
6792,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein chor ka hath baghair lakdi ke chamdey ki dhaal ya aam dhaal ki chori par hi kaataa jata tha. ham se Usman ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan ne bayan kya, unse Hisham ne bayan kya, unse unke walid ne, unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne isi tarah ( bayan kya ( ."
6793,"chor ka hath lakdi ke chamdey ki dhaal ya aam dhaal ki qeemat se kam par nahi kaataa jata tha. ye donon dhaal qeemat se miltii thin. uski riwayat Wakee aur ibne-Idrees ne Hisham ke waastey se ki, unse unke walid ne mursalan riwayat kya."
6794,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein chor ka hath dhaal ki qeemat se kam par nahi kaataa jata tha. lakdi ke chamdey ki dhaal ho ya aam dhaal, ye donon cheezein qeemat wali thin."
6795,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dhaal par hath kaataa tha jiski qeemat teen dirham thi.
6796,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dhaal ki chori par hath kaataa tha jiski qeemat teen dirham thi.
6797,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik dhaal par hath kaataa tha jiski qeemat teen dirham thi.
6798,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik chor ka hath aik dhaal par kaataa tha jiski qeemat teen dirham thi, is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin Ishaq ne ki aur Leis ne bayan kya ke mujh se Naafe ne ( ثمنه (ke bajaey) lafz ( قيمته ( kaha,"
6799,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne chor par laanat ki hai ke aik andaa churaataa hai aur iska hath kaataa jata hai, aik rassii churaataa hai aur uska hath kaataa jata hai."
6800,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aurat ka hath katwaayaa. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke wo aurat baad mein bhi aati thi aur main uski zarooratein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rakhti thi, us aurat ne tauba kar li thi aur Hasan tauba ka saboot diya tha."
6801,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik jamat ke sath bait ki thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke main tum se ahad leta hun ke tum Allah ka kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraaogey, tum chori nahi karogey, apni aulad ki jaan nahi logey , apne dil se ghad kar kisi par tohmat nahi lagaaogey aur nek kaamon mein meri nafarmani na karogey. to tum mein se jo koi waadey pura karega uska sawab Allah ke uper lazim hai aur jo koi unmein se kuchh ghalati kar guzrega aur duniya mein hi usey uski saza mil jaeygi to ye uska kaffara hogi aur usey paak karne wali hogi aur jiski ghalati ko Allah chipa lega to uska mamla Allah ke sath hai, chahey to usey azab de aur chahey to uski maghfirat kar de. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke hath katney ke baad agar chor ne tauba kar li to uski gawahi qabool hogi. yahi haal har us shakhs ka hai jis par had jari ki gaee ho ke agar wo tauba kar lega to uski gawahi qabool ki jaeygi."
